title: Rosewill Aluminum 3.5-Inch Silver USB 2.0 External Enclosure Cooling RX35-AT-SU SLV Silver
description: Convert your 3.5" SATA hard drive into a portable external drive with Rosewill's RX35-AT-SU hard drive enclosure. Use it to store your documents, photos, media files, and backup your important data. This USB 2.0 external enclosure features high-quality aluminum construction, LED indicators for Power/HDD status and a slim, glossy design with desktop stand included. The Rosewill RX35-AT-SU is compatible with 3.5-inch SATA hard drives, offering an ideal solution for your external storage needs. The USB 2.0 interface enables data transfer speeds of up to 480Mbps while maintaining backward compatibility with USB 1.1. Support for plug-and-play significantly eliminates the need for driver installations. The lightweight aluminum casing delivers excellent heat dissipation and provides tough, reliable hard drive protection.
